data.description: You'll feel right at home in this three bedroom, 2 bath home, setting in the country. Features include a living room with double widows, a den with a fireplace and large windows, an open dining room/ kitchen with French doors leading out to a back deck overlooking the backyard, and a large primary bedroom and attached bath with a garden tub. Call and schedule a tour today!
